Descargar e instalar Nodejs:

https://nodejs.org/es/

Instalar homebrew en terminal:

/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

Añadir la extensión de Reactjs a chrome:

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/react-developer-tools/fmkadmapgofadopljbjfkapdkoienihi?hl=es

Instalar Yarn:

https://classic.yarnpkg.com/es-ES/docs/install#debian-stable

Plugins en Visual code:

Bracket Pair Colorizer

ES7 React/Redux/GraphQL/React-Native snippets

ESLint

Material icon theme

Night owl

Path Intellisense

Prettier - Code formatter

Simple React Snippets

Instalar npm y npx:

sudo apt-get install nodejs

sudo apt-get install npm

sudo npm i -g npx









